{"word":"Ekron","slug":"ekron","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ekron</b> <a href=\"#/H6138\">H6138</a> <br/> One of the five chief cities of the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=3'>Jos 13:3</a><br/> Conquered and allotted to Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=11'>Jos 15:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=45'>Jos 15:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=18'>Jdg 1:18</a><br/> Allotted to Dan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=43'>Jos 19:43</a><br/> The ark of God taken to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=5&verse=10'>1Sa 5:10</a><br/> Temple of Baal-Zebub at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=2'>2Ki 1:2</a><br/> Prophecies against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=20'>Jer 25:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=8'>Amo 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=2&verse=4'>Zep 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=5'>Zec 9:5</a>"}]}